      .header__btn
        a.btn.btn--accent(href="#{data.repo}#readme" data-block="readme") Getting Started
        small Installation guide for developers

      .header__btn.header__download
        span.btn
          | Download
          icon(name="ei-chevron-down")
          select(data-block="download")
            option(disabled selected) Choose format:
            option(value="#{data.downloadLocation}/evil-icons.svg.zip") SVG
            option(value="#{data.downloadLocation}/evil-icons.ai") Illustrator CC
            option(value="#{data.downloadLocation}/evil-icons-cs.ai") Illustrator CS
